  <h2>The Bottom Line: Process Over Luck</h2>



  <p>The difference between traders who consistently find 100x meme coins and those who don't isn't luck ” it's process. The framework outlined here turns meme coin research from a guessing game into a repeatable, measurable system. Does it guarantee results? Absolutely not. Does it dramatically improve your odds? The data says yes.</p>



  <p>Start small. Score 10 tokens per day using this framework without trading any of them. After a week, analyze which scores correlated with actual price action. Refine your weightings. Then start deploying capital ” cautiously, with strict position sizing, and always with the understanding that in meme coins, survival is the true superpower.</p>



